-- EDP Renovaveis Obtains Four Power Purchase Agreements in Brazil
-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 2011-12-21T08:24:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-21/edp-renovaveis-obtains-four-power-purchase-agreements-in-brazil.html
EDP Renovaveis SA (EDPR) , the renewable-
energy unit of Portuguese utility EDP-Energias de Portugal SA,
said it was awarded four power purchase agreements for a 20-year
period at an energy auction in  Brazil .  The power purchase agreements will be used for energy
produced by four wind farms that will be installed in the
Brazilian state of Rio Grande do Norte, EDP Renovaveis said last
night in a regulatory filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joao Lima at 
 jlima1@bloomberg.net  